Copper fell in London after a report
that the  European Central Bank  wants to expand assistance to
 Italy , heightening speculation that sovereign debt in  Europe 
will curb economic growth and metal demand.  Market News:  Metals News:  Metals Prices:  To contact the reporter on this story:
